{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Reimburse excess VED paid for campervan/motor homes from Sept 19 to Mar 20",
        "additional_details": "The VED that is charged for vehicles registered between September 2019 and March 2020 should be the same as all other vehicles in their class. They should be brought in line and the excess revenue collected be returned to the owners where possible.",
        "background": "While the Government has now reduced annual VED liabilities for most new motorhomes to a flat rate, from September 2019 to March 2020 newly registered motorhomes were liable for VED of up to \u00a32,135. All owners affected should be also be reimbursed the difference.",
